        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 16:04:56 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 16:04:56 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Jeff Arnold, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/20/how-do-donald-trump-kamala-harris-net-worths-compare.webp" alt="How do Donald Trump, Kamala Harris' net worths compare?" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">How do Donald Trump, Kamala Harris' net worths compare?</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Donald Trump and Kamala Harris approach politics differently but have also taken opposite roads to personal wealth.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/20/how-do-donald-trump-kamala-harris-net-worths-compare/"  >(Jeff Arnold, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 18:17:09 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 18:17:09 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Christine Samra, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/20/beyonce-launches-new-whisky.webp" alt="Beyonc&#233; launches new whisky" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Beyonc&#233; launches new whisky</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The name honors Beyoncé's paternal great-grandfather Davis Hogue, who was a farmer and a moonshiner during Prohibition.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/20/beyonce-launches-new-whisky/"  >(Christine Samra, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 19:06:27 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 19:06:27 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Brett Samuels, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/20/ex-trump-aide-grisham-among-gop-speakers-expected-to-address-dnc.webp" alt="Ex-Trump aide Grisham among GOP speakers expected to address DNC" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Ex-Trump aide Grisham among GOP speakers expected to address DNC</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Former Trump White House press secretary Stephanie Grisham will speak at the Democratic National Convention this week in Chicago, shortly after becoming one of the highest-profile Republican critics of former President Trump to back Vice President Harris.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/20/ex-trump-aide-grisham-among-gop-speakers-expected-to-address-dnc/"  >(Brett Samuels, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 18:22:41 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 18:22:41 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/20/ruth-johnson-colvin-who-founded-literacy-volunteers-of-america-has-died-at-107.webp" alt="Ruth Johnson Colvin, who founded Literacy Volunteers of America, has died at 107" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Ruth Johnson Colvin, who founded Literacy Volunteers of America, has died at 107</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Ruth Johnson Colvin, who founded Literacy Volunteers of America, was inducted into the National Women's Hall of Fame and received the nation’s highest civilian award, the Presidential Medal of Freedom, has died. She was 107 years old.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/20/ruth-johnson-colvin-who-founded-literacy-volunteers-of-america-has-died-at-107/"  >(The Associated Press, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 19:05:07 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 19:05:07 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Bill Disbrow, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/20/dncs-second-night-to-feature-obamas-swing-state-democrats.webp" alt="Barack and Michelle Obama close DNC's second night with 'fired up' speeches" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Barack and Michelle Obama close DNC's second night with 'fired up' speeches</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Headlining Tuesday night will be former President Barack Obama, Michelle Obama and second gentleman Doug Emhoff.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/20/dncs-second-night-to-feature-obamas-swing-state-democrats/"  >(Bill Disbrow, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 23:12:58 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 23:12:58 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="ROB GILLIES and JOSH FUNK, Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/20/canadian-freight-trains-could-stop-moving-thursday-if-they-do-many-businesses-will-be-hurt.webp" alt="Canadian freight trains could stop moving Thursday. If they do, many businesses will be hurt" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Canadian freight trains could stop moving Thursday. If they do, many businesses will be hurt</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      TORONTO (AP) — Businesses across a variety of industries are bracing for freight trains to stop moving Thursday at both major Canadian freight railroads if they can’t resolve a contract dispute with the union that represents engineers, conductors and dispatchers.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/20/canadian-freight-trains-could-stop-moving-thursday-if-they-do-many-businesses-will-be-hurt/"  >(ROB GILLIES and JOSH FUNK, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:56:04 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 20:56:04 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Iman Palm, KTLA 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/08/21/chick-fil-a-to-launch-streaming-service-featuring-family-friendly-shows-report.webp" alt="Chick-fil-A to launch streaming service featuring family-friendly shows: report" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Chick-fil-A to launch streaming service featuring family-friendly shows: report</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Chick-fil-A, the Georgia-based restaurant chain known for its chicken sandwiches and waffle fries, has plans to launch a streaming service. Chick-fil-A has reportedly been working with multiple production companies and studios to create family-friendly shows, especially in reality television.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/08/21/chick-fil-a-to-launch-streaming-service-featuring-family-friendly-shows-report/"  >(Iman Palm, KTLA 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/world/">Around the world</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 07:13:24 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 07:13:24 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, KPRC 2">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/21/moscow-comes-under-largest-ukrainian-drone-attack-yet-but-destroys-them-all-russian-authorities-say.webp" alt="Moscow sees one of Ukraine's largest drone attacks as fighting rages in Kursk and eastern Ukraine" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Moscow sees one of Ukraine's largest drone attacks as fighting rages in Kursk and eastern Ukraine</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Russian authorities say Moscow has come under one of the largest attacks by Ukrainian drones since the start of fighting in 2022, and that it destroyed all of them.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/21/moscow-comes-under-largest-ukrainian-drone-attack-yet-but-destroys-them-all-russian-authorities-say/"  >(Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 22 Aug 2024 03:47:13 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 22 Aug 2024 03:47:13 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="JON GAMBRELL, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/22/commercial-ship-not-under-command-after-repeated-attacks-target-it-in-red-sea-british-say.webp" alt="Greek oil tanker drifting and ablaze after repeated attacks in the Red Sea, British military says" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Greek oil tanker drifting and ablaze after repeated attacks in the Red Sea, British military says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      DUBAI, United Arab Emirates (AP) — A Greek-flagged oil tanker traveling through the Red Sea came under repeated attack Wednesday, leaving the vessel “not under command” and drifting ablaze after an assault suspected to have been carried out by Yemen's Houthi rebels, the British military said.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/22/commercial-ship-not-under-command-after-repeated-attacks-target-it-in-red-sea-british-say/"  >(JON GAMBRELL, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:04:52 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:04:52 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="SONIA PÉREZ D., Associated Press, PIX 11">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/22/guatemalan-police-arrest-7-accused-of-trafficking-the-53-migrants-who-asphyxiated-in-texas-in-2022.webp" alt="Guatemalan police arrest 7 accused of trafficking the 53 migrants who asphyxiated in Texas in 2022" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Guatemalan police arrest 7 accused of trafficking the 53 migrants who asphyxiated in Texas in 2022</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      GUATEMALA CITY (AP) — Guatemalan police on Wednesday arrested seven Guatemalans accused of having smuggled 53 migrants from Mexico and Central America who died of asphyxiation in 2022 in Texas after being abandoned in a tractor trailer in the scorching summer heat.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/22/guatemalan-police-arrest-7-accused-of-trafficking-the-53-migrants-who-asphyxiated-in-texas-in-2022/"  >(SONIA PÉREZ D., Associated Press, PIX 11)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 07:12:17 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 07:12:17 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Stephen Mcgrath And Andreea Alexandru, Associated Press, Local 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/21/police-raid-andrew-tates-home-in-romania-as-new-allegations-emerge-involving-minors.webp" alt="Police raid Andrew Tate's home in Romania as new allegations emerge involving minors" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Police raid Andrew Tate's home in Romania as new allegations emerge involving minors</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Masked police officers in Romania have carried out fresh raids at the home of internet influencer Andrew Tate, who is awaiting trial on charges of human trafficking, rape and forming a criminal gang to sexually exploit women.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/21/police-raid-andrew-tates-home-in-romania-as-new-allegations-emerge-involving-minors/"  >(Stephen Mcgrath And Andreea Alexandru, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:36:20 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 17:36:20 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Tom Dempsey, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/21/cease-fire-proposal-talks-deadlocked.webp" alt="Cease-fire talks deadlocked as Hamas won't agree to proposal: Egypt" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Cease-fire talks deadlocked as Hamas won't agree to proposal: Egypt</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Diplomatic efforts to reach a cease-fire between Israel and Hamas had redoubled as fears grow of a wider regional war.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/21/cease-fire-proposal-talks-deadlocked/"  >(Tom Dempsey, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 00:16:59 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 21 Aug 2024 00:16:59 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Anna Kutz, NewsNation">
