  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/08/21/wilmer-puello-mota-russian-army.webp" alt="US veteran wanted for child porn appears in Russian propaganda" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">US veteran wanted for child porn appears in Russian propaganda</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Wilmer Puello-Mota, a United States Air Force veteran, said, "I don't consider myself a traitor" in the video.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/08/21/wilmer-puello-mota-russian-army/"  >(Anna Kutz, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
