    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/19/favorable-views-of-harris-have-risen-this-summer-heading-into-the-dnc-poll.webp" alt="Favorable views of Harris have risen this summer heading into the DNC: Poll" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Favorable views of Harris have risen this summer heading into the DNC: Poll</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Vice President Kamala Harris is entering the Democratic National Convention with increased excitement from Democrats and a steady rise in her favorability ratings among Americans as a whole.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/19/favorable-views-of-harris-have-risen-this-summer-heading-into-the-dnc-poll/"  >(The Associated Press, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:46:17 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 11:46:17 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Alexander Bolton, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/20/republicans-worry-trump-blowing-their-chances-for-senate-majority.webp" alt="Republicans worry Trump blowing their chances for Senate majority" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Republicans worry Trump blowing their chances for Senate majority</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Even Sen. Lindsey Graham, one of Trump’s top allies in the Senate, is urging the former president to tone down his “showman” streak at rallies.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/20/republicans-worry-trump-blowing-their-chances-for-senate-majority/"  >(Alexander Bolton, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 00:20:47 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 20 Aug 2024 00:20:47 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Alonzo Small, WGN 9">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/08/20/lt-gov-stratton-biden-among-most-effective-presidents-harris-best-to-defeat-trump.webp" alt="Lt. Gov Stratton: Biden among most effective presidents; Harris best to defeat Trump" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Lt. Gov Stratton: Biden among most effective presidents; Harris best to defeat Trump</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      As a Black woman in politics, Stratton says she isn't pulling for Harris solely because of the history behind her nomination.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/08/20/lt-gov-stratton-biden-among-most-effective-presidents-harris-best-to-defeat-trump/"  >(Alonzo Small, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset></main>
